7. User’s Rights to User’s Information
7.1. You have the right to be informed about the collection and use of your personal data. You have the right to access your personal data and have it corrected if it is wrong or incomplete. You have the right to restrict the processing of your data where the accuracy of your personal data is contested, where the processing is unlawful, and where Persona Game Studio no longer needs the personal data for the purposes for which Persona Game Studio has processed it. You have the right to object to the processing of your personal data and also restrict its processing in those instances where Persona Game Studio undertook processing of it in carrying out a task in the public interest or where necessary for our legitimate interest where there is no compelling reason for its continued processing. You have the right to withdraw consent that you have given to the collection and processing of your personal data at any time. If you do withdraw your consent to the collection and processing of your personal data, that withdrawal shall not affect the lawfulness of any processing by Persona Game Studio that is based on the consent you have given before you withdrew it. You also have the right to obtain the deletion of your data when it is no longer relevant to the purposes for which it was collected or processed, when you have withdrawn consent and there is no basis for us to continue processing, when you have objected to further processing and there is no compelling interest for continued processing, and when the data was unlawfully processed.
7.2. The Users can, in particular, exercise their rights as follows:
7.2.1. The User may opt out of receiving promotional communications, such as marketing emails from us by following the instructions in such communications. The updated settings may not be effective immediately. Note that the User may still continue to receive non-promotional communications from us, such as communications regarding the Application or updates to our Persona Game Studio Terms of Service or this Privacy Policy.
7.2.2. We may send the User push notifications through the Applications. The User may at any time opt-out from receiving these types of communications by changing the settings on the corresponding device.
7.2.3. The User can opt-out of interest-based advertising on mobile applications by checking the privacy settings of the corresponding Android or iOS device and turning off “Allow Apps to Request to Track” or selecting "Limit Ad Tracking" (Apple iOS) or "Opt-out of Interest Based Ads" (Android).
7.2.4. Upon request, we can provide the User a copy of the User’s personal data in an electronic format.
7.2.5. Upon request, we may delete or change the User's personal data. Note that if you ask us to remove your personal data, we will retain your data as necessary for our legitimate business interests, such as to comply with our legal obligations, resolve disputes, and enforce our agreements.
7.2. These rights may be exercised by contacting Persona Game Studio with your specific request via email indicated below. Persona Game Studio will address any such requests in a timely manner. In certain cases, Persona Game Studio may ask you to verify your identity before acting on your request. If you are unsatisfied with Persona Game Studio’s response, you may refer your complaint to the relevant supervisory authority in your jurisdiction.
